Requirements:

perl 5.10.1

To install do something like:

export CCFLAGS="-I/Users/bernhard/sw/include"
export LDDFLAGS="-L/Users/bernhard/sw/lib"

perl Makefile.PL

make 
make install

If broccoli.h is not found (many unknown defitnition), check CCFLAGS. If scripts complain about dynamic linking errors on start, check LDDFLAGS.

